<h2>Minneapolis Energy Incentives</h2>
<p>Minneapolis residents have access to substantial incentives for both solar and HVAC upgrades. The federal Investment Tax Credit provides 30% of solar installation costs as a tax credit through 2032, then stepping down to 26% in 2033 and 22% in 2034. Minnesota offers additional state incentives including a solar sales tax exemption and property tax exemption for solar installations, meaning the added home value from solar doesn't increase property taxes.</p>

